snippet: David Moyes admitted he was "very happy" after overseeing his maiden victory as Real Sociedad coach before criticising the Spanish referee for what the Scot suggested was excessive zeal....

headline.print_headline: Moyes Critical of 'Overzealous' Referee After Debut Win
headline.main: Moyes Critical of 'Overzealous' Referee After Debut Win

lead_paragraph: David Moyes admitted he was "very happy" after overseeing his maiden victory as Real Sociedad coach before criticising the Spanish referee for what the Scot suggested was excessive zeal.
